title: My Channel Logos XL & TunerSalad 32 for Windows Media Center
description:
Please let the developer know you appreciate his work by making a donation if you can afford to do so.

Compatible with Windows 7, Windows 8, and Windows 8.1.

MCL XL lets you:
 Automatically download and add logos to your guide page.
 Use new XL logos which are 25% wider than MCL v2.
 Add your own logos where one is not provided.
 Increase visible guide from 7 rows to 12 rows.
 Increase visible guide from 2 hours to 3 hours.
 Increase visible mini-guide from 2 rows to 4 rows.

TunerSalad 32 lets you increase your TV tuner limit from 4 to 32.
